('rec1sNUjN9EvVCTzR','Drees & Sommer','Watchlist','Capital Projects / Real Estate Engineering Consultancy','investor_pe','Private','Stuttgart, Germany',null,'https://www.dreso.com',null,null,null,null,null,null,'Major German engineering and project management consultancy with substantial real estate and infrastructure capital projects practice. Geographic logic alone makes a DACH-region capital projects firm a near-certain Accenture target — Frankfurt, Berlin, and broader European hyperscaler activity require local presence. Drees & Sommer profile fits the Soben/BOSLAN/IQT pattern: specialist regional engineering shop with capital projects depth. Lower probability target than Tier-1 acquisitions, but high probability for the geographic completion thesis.',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'["D10 — Construction", "D14 — Real Estate & Site Selection", "D11 — Sustainability"]'::jsonb,'Airtable Manual','2026-04-27'::date),
